      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"8. ELLSWORTH got around the 400m at this track to take a TG1-4W in a solid 22.85 for a 4.5 lengths win. Hot win latest and looks the one to beat again. 1. ZIPPING BELUGA was checked in the run and safely held when fifth (23.22) in a Grade 6 over 400m at this track. Gets chance to atone. 4. RED BROOK produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at Angle Park over 530m behind Victa Wally (31.33) in a Grade 6. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Should be about the mark. 2. ZIPPING THERON can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.\",\"runners\":[8,1,4,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
